        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hi, I'm Oluwaseye Oyadiran</h1>
            <p>
                I am a Nigerian-born tech professional and aspiring serial entrepreneur, currently building my career in the United States. My foundation was solidified with a Bachelor's in Computer Science, where I complemented my academic studies with hands-on experience through internships at various companies. This unique blend of rigorous technical education and practical industry exposure has equipped me with a comprehensive skill set. Now, I am focused on channeling this expertise, along with a growing business acumen, to identify market opportunities and build innovative solutions. My ultimate goal is to transition from a tech professional into a successful serial entrepreneur, creating ventures that make a meaningful impact.
            </p>

            <h2>Life Categories</h2>
            <div class="life-categories">
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Entry Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Professional Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Personal Life</h3></div>
                <div class="category-card"><h3>Philanthropy</h3></div>
            </div>

            <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>